ying it to several publicly available ontologies containing swrl rules we demonstrate that our analysis and visualization approach allows users to quickly examine logical relationships in such rule bases full pdf version available here view the phenologue project back to search results information last updated tue apr 5 2011 make corrections to this publication go stanford biomedical infomatics only all of stanford school of medicine contact information maps & information site map stanford university
